title: Bug 116564: Title of hyperlink builder changes to incorrect value
description:
<BUG REPORT>
{'id': '116564', 'title': 'Bug 116564The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', now it changes with settings.', 'description': '', 'OB': 'Click on 'OK' then reopen hyperlink builder.Actual result: its title becomes 'www.actuate.com'.Expected result: hyperlinke builder title should be 'Hyperlink Options'. ', 'EB': '', 'SR': ''}
</BUG REPORT>
OB: When the user clicks on 'OK' and then reopens the hyperlink builder, the actual title displayed is 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected behavior is that the title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Open the hyperlink builder.
2. Make changes to the settings.
3. Click on 'OK'.
4. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
